The '''Pokéball''' is a type of [[Pokéballs|pokéball]]. It automatically tries to catch a wild Pokémon after defeating it if it or a higher type of pokéball is active.


==Details==
===Description===
A basic pokéball to capture Pokémon with. It has no catch rate multipliers.

